{"tid":2507485,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"[義教回饋連登] 義教連登結他巴絲","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T00:55:09.000Z","uid":56674,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7866311e1214b4e68147a7028eaeff1f15d327","tid":2507485,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係蘭調人，我係一個全職既結他老師，有任何野想問我可以透過telegram搵到我： <a href=\"https://t.me/Guitar_ABC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGuitar_ABC&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0slSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=bf6c311f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Guitar_ABC</a><br />\n<br />\n同時間我連載緊既樂理拙文：<br />\n1. 《2020年代香港流行曲和弦編曲賞析》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2477735/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2477735/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 和弦旋律分析Q&amp;A<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2499411/page/1?post=bf71a23786a2d2b2b614939c140ff98baaea8bba\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2499411/page/1?post=bf71a23786a2d2b2b614939c140ff98baaea8bba</a><br />\n<br />\n細佬我將會再次回饋連登，舉行每星期一至兩次的<span class=\"gold\">義教</span>連登巴絲結他課堂。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n－適合新手／卡樽頸已久的連登結他巴絲<br />\n－電／木結他皆可<br />\n－任何風格（我識答既就答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n－因為以前做過幾次都有放飛機既人，所以每星期只有固定兩日可選（響細佬我平時教班既節數之間或之後）<br />\n－每人可以黎最多1次<br />\n－響葵興，我的教室<br />\n－土地問題，所以每次最多1對1或1對2<br />\n－自攜結他同彈過既譜／notes<br />\n－由即日起可以報名，完結時間另行通知<br />\n－時段：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">星期三－6pm 7pm 8pm<br />\n星期六－3pm 4pm<br />\n星期日－10am 11am</span></strong><br />\n<ins><span class=\"blue\">其他時間再可以睇睇，有時可能得</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概會講既內容：<br />\n1. 流行結他（即係普通彈唱）－中階<br />\n－點樣可以無perfect pitch，用結他指板可以搵到一首歌既key<br />\n－點樣可以執到譜／chord／識得分網上簡譜執得岩唔岩<br />\n－點樣可以彈得似原本果首歌多一啲<br />\n－掃法／勾法變化<br />\n－結他編曲編chord<br />\n－知道歌係點寫出黎<br />\n－更多內容未能一一盡錄<br />\n<br />\n2. Blues（電結他soloing）<br />\n－基本shuffle blues soloing方法：用arpeggios/chord tone，而非pentatonics<br />\n－基本 12 bar blues comping，minor blues同shuffle blues<br />\n－大師風格剖析簡介，主要3 Kings，Jimi，Clapton，SRV<br />\n－Playing sometimes outside，如何更改12-bar blues progression內的chord產生新的outside soloing line<br />\n－standard licks and runs in both major/minor pentatonic scale<br />\n－點樣調教amp既EQ／結他上的pot value／用咩effect去拎到一個標準tone<br />\n<br />\n3. Jazz Guitar<br />\n－練習Routine：於固定把位上將chord shapes/arpeggios 沿circle of Vth彈奏<br />\n－Comping：隨住fake book上的chord將一隻jazz standard完整comp出（用chord fragment同特定rhythm有脈絡地一個接一個彈出）<br />\n－分析chord progression in any jazz standards：響任何的standard上solo或comp前都必需要做的一步<br />\n－正確基本3大modes：Ionian，Dorian，Mixolydian<br />\n－ii - V - I 於 bebop/jazz guitar soloing的標準彈奏方法／chord擺法<br />\n－太多未能一一盡錄<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴絲可以tg直接聯絡我：<a href=\"https://t.me/Guitar_ABC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGuitar_ABC&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0slSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=bf6c311f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Guitar_ABC</a>"},{"pid":"5b034dc177a0ebcae2d71786ff83f15d533538a3","tid":2507485,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T14:03:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0494ddce4fec5ed1365631db2927db169906d12a","tid":2507485,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd345226767ee96f5bcba0e1351cc9649b976bea","tid":2507485,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2719e0429b03a34a3b50c2b3e1e24a3548e36917","tid":2507485,"uid":56674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a739410b65640cbe3405853e85923f29440f336f","tid":2507485,"uid":105017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"本身識彈d結他<br />\n完全唔識blues<br />\n點樣接觸同理解blues